




Mizuho Bank and Mizuho Corporate Bank has mergered.












































On July 1, 2013, Mizuho Bank and Mizuho Corporate Bank merged and began operating as the new Mizuho Bank.
As a result of the merger, our website address has been changed.
Please click on the following link to access the website of the new Mizuho Bank:

（https://www.mizuhobank.com/）
If you have bookmarked the website of the former Mizuho Corporate Bank, or added it to your "favorites" folder, please replace it with the above address.

