Mizuho Bank, Ltd. Key Developments

Mizuho Bank, Ltd. Announces Executive Changes
Jul 3 17
Mizuho Bank, Ltd. changed the position of Yasuhiko Hashimoto from Executive Officer, Joint Head of Europe, Middle East and Africa, and General Manager of Europe Structured Finance Department to Executive Officer, Joint Head of Europe, Middle East and Africa effective as of July 3, 2017.


Mizuho Bank, Ltd. Announces Management Changes
Jun 22 17
Mizuho Bank, Ltd. changed the position of Yasuyuki Shibata from Executive Officer, General Manager of Risk Management Department to Executive Managing Director and Managing Executive Officer and Head of Risk Management Group. The company changed the position of Ryusuke Aya from  Executive Managing Director and Managing Executive Officer and Head of Risk Management Group to Member of the Board of Directors (Audit & Supervisory Committee Member) effective as of June 23, 2017.


Mizuho Bank Presents at Global Expansion Summit, Jun-19-2017 02:30 PM
Jun 13 17
Mizuho Bank Presents at Global Expansion Summit, Jun-19-2017 02:30 PM. Venue: Intercontinental 02, London, United Kingdom. Speakers: Mary Stokes, Associate Director, Country and Sovereign Risk.


