Mizuho Bank to Open Local Bank in Mexico
Dec 24 15
Mizuho Bank announced it has obtained permission from Mexico's financial authority to establish a bank in the Latin American country. With the approval, the banking unit of Mizuho Financial Group Inc. will upgrade its local representative office in Mexico City. It aims to open the new bank in the first half of fiscal 2016.


